import { Container, Grid } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

const Profile = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Grid container spacing={3}>
                    <Grid item md={4} sm={12}>lol</Grid>
                    <Grid item md={8} sm={12}>lol</Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default Profile
